snippet.title: Skid Row - Wasted Time (At O'Shucks Karaoke Bar, FL)
snippet.description:
#orlando #karaoke

Siegfried Song Facebook : http://www.facebook.com/SiegfriedSongOfficial

Sometimes, I’m pushed forward by someone’s encouragement, but in the end, it’s always me who has to step onto the stage.

Before singing, I ask myself: Is my condition okay? Does this song fit the atmosphere? Will the monitoring be good? But the answer is always the same—I’ll never know until I try.

Whether it’s a karaoke where country songs dominate, a stage where I can’t hear anything, or a day when I’m in the worst condition, I’m the one standing there. And I have to accept it.
